iv class="container"> <h2>The REIGNITE<span class="tm">™</span> <span>Phase Gates</span></h2> <p class="section-sub">A staged build sequence where each gate de-risks the next move before scale.</p> <div class="diagram-placeholder"><p><strong>Diagram Placeholder:</strong> Process Visual (Phase Gates) — scheduled for Final Diagram Sprint.</p></div> </div> </section> <section class="framework" id="architecture">
